1 this series is vastly underrated . like many others , i came upon farscape after the series had been cancelled . bought season 1 and was surprised to find a smartly written drama infused with a balanced mix of suspense , romance , wit and , of course , sci - fi . right off the bat it got a 10 for being the first series or movie to satisfy us how our hero - and every alien with whom he comes in contact - speaks english ! okay , a few others have skirted the issue , but farscape did it the best . the point is , the writers pay close attention to detail to make the show as believable as possible.<br /><br />with so much bad programming out there , it 's a shame that balanced , entertaining series such as farscape do n't get enough exposure and recognition to stay in production . while we enjoy the four seasons and , thankfully , the four - hour miniseries , maybe we can make enough noise to convince the producers to continue the show .
