1 a real surprise . not exactly family entertainment from " disney " . some violence , lots of tense moments , and a great story , based on fact . the theme of " night crossing " is , determination wins . never losing sight of their objective , two east german families risk it all , in their daring balloon escape to freedom . the story is both harrowing and heartwarming . time is not on their side . the east german police are closing in and the outcome far from certain , until the very end . if you are looking for a good evenings entertainment , that contains no nudity , and limited violence , then i highly recommend " night crossing " . it is pure entertainment . - merk
